{"word":"G4280 - προερέω - proeréō - pro-er-eh'-o - Foretell","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προερέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">proeréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro-er-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Foretell</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முன்னறிவி, முன்னே சொல்"},{"paragraph":"to say already, predict"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2046 - ἐρέω - eréō - er-eh'-o/2046\">G2046</a>; used as alternate of <a href=\"#/G4277 - προέπω - proépō - pro-ep'-o/4277\">G4277</a>; to <i>say already</i>, <i>predict:</i> - foretell, say (speak, tell) before.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}